multiply by adding a0: i32 and b0: i32 gives i32:
  track total: i32 from 0
  track outer: i32 from 0
  while outer is less than b0:
    track inner: i32 from 0
    while inner is less than a0:
      total becomes total plus 1
      inner becomes inner plus 1
    outer becomes outer plus 1
  total

main gives i32:
  multiply by adding 6 and 7
